Here's why you sue

So these MFs will cease and desist lying as political propaganda.

We MUST make them stop. They MUST be stopped from lying through the courts. You make a vicious example of out of someone like Grohl. You erase a decade of his earnings.

Think about it.

Requirements for Defamation and how it applies to Grohl

1. A False Statement of Fact Was Made

Grohl knows that he does not OWN the rights to his song. He made the deal with BMI and now THEY own his song, not him. He cannot say who can and cannot use his songs at venues. If he didn't like that, well he's a fucking galactic tard for signing that contract.

2. The Statement Was Communicated to a Third Party

He told the media. It's all over the media. He made a public statement. He is a public person who made a false statement. And it was syndicated all over media in order to HARM TRUMP and his campaign

3. The Defendant Was Negligent or Acted With Absolute Malice in Determining the Truth of the Statement

  • A) Grohl is a low intellect goofus who doesn't understand what he himself signed, and was negligent. CHECK

  • B) Grohl made his statements on purpose to harm Trump (acted with malice) and also to i) Blame, ii) Shame, iii) Defame Trump supporters -- CHECK

4. The Statement Was Not Privileged

Is Grohl a foreign diplomat? no. Is Grohl CIA? unknown doctor. Is Grohl making a statement on behalf of derpartment of derfence? no. Doe Grohl have a security clearance he's using to make this statement? no.

NOT PRIVILEGED >>>

5. The Statement Caused Some Type of Damage

There is no doubt that his statement harmed the Trump Campaign by insinuating that they are lawless and thieving (stealing music), and that their use of the song has HARMED ARTISTS.

This idea of misusing copyrighted material harming artists repels people and acts to intimidate voters and chill future speech (in this case, using other people's songs is a form of speech / expression)

The ENTIRE point of Grohl making this statement was TO CAUSE HARM TO TRUMP and Trump supporters by chilling their speech/expression (use of songs) by way of the threat of lawfare.

And to make them look bad in the eyes of the voting public.

Therefore, the only responsible thing for the Trump Campaign to do is to sue David Grohl and make an absolute example out of him so that there are no more whiny liberal David Grohls making grossly negligent and malicious political statements when it is a critical time for them to actually shut the fuck up.

Furthermore, I would actually try to make a criminal referral to the DOJ of ***INTIMTIDATION OF VOTERS 18 U.S. Code § 594 - Intimidation of voters ***and have him criminally charged

  • https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/18/594

In his defamatory and grossly negligent and malicious statements, he's interfering with the elections to a much greater degree than Russia ever did, if they even DID interfere with our elections.

Thanks for hearing my rant. It's the most I can do, since I can't fly over to david grohls place and eye-laser his cock off
